          Learning a little at a time and building in complexity as the book moves forward. Both theory and 
          practice driving your knowledge.
          </p>
          <p>
          If you are a beginner and looking to learn Ruby on Rails, the purpose of this book is to simply
          get you there in small, manageable steps.
          </p>
